    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "A new traveler, eh? Want to learn how to hunt? The #b#o1#s#k you see here are normally too powerful for you to handle, but #p313#, the head of all magicians, sealed up their power. So take down three, pick up what they drop, and go see #b#p6##k, who should be around here somewhere."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Look at your minimap (#bM#k), located at the top left corner of the screen. You should see something green blinking on the northeast side of the map. That's #b#p6##k. You'll run into Jr. Sentinels on your way to meet #b#p6##k. Defeat them, pick up 3 #t4000000#, then talk to #b#p6##k."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Oh, you know how to hunt already? Well, you can still test your abilities!"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Are you the one #p7# is training? He mentioned you... Let's see if you've trained correctly."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Someday, long after you leave this place, you'll be powerful enough to take on real Jr. Sentinels. Oh, and when you level up, check your #bAbility Points#k in your Character Info. \nTo move on to the next map, either press the #bup arrow key#k in front of the portal to the right or just talk to me again."
        }
